      kny_day2_label: 'Virak Wanabat \u2014 \u179c\u17b7\u179a:\u179c\u17d0\u1793\u1794\u178f',
      kny_day2_date: 'Dag 2 \u00b7 14 april',
      kny_day2_p: 'Andra dagen \u00e4r tillgnad v\u00e4lg\u00f6renhet. Familjer bygger <strong>sandkullar</strong> (\u1797\u17d2\u1793\u17c6\u1781\u17d2\u179f\u17b6\u1785\u17cb) vid tempel.',
      kny_day3_label: 'Tngai Leang Sak \u2014 \u1790\u17d2\u1784\u17c3\u179b\u17be\u1784\u179f\u1780',
      kny_day3_date: 'Dag 3 \u00b7 15\u201316 april',
      kny_day3_p: 'Sista dagen \u00e4r den heligaste. Buddhister badar <strong>Buddhastatyer</strong> med parfymerat vatten.',
